description: Everyone in Wilmington knows that there’s no better way to celebrate any occasion than with Cajun Sno!This truck has been treating the locals with Nola-style Snoballs (they’re not spicy but they’re still authentic) since 2013. These perfectly fluffy icy cajun concoctions soak in fun, unique flavors like no other!You’ll find Red Hot, Tiger’s Blood, and all your faves...So when you see the gator on this truck go by, it’s just a friendly reminder to come out now or later, say hi, and give these crazy refreshing Cajun Snoballs a try!
name: Cajun-Sno
